# 🔥 问题 3：upstreamCode 解析太“天真”

```ts
const detectUpstreamCode = (responseBody: string)
```

---

## 💥 问题

你只解析：

```ts
parsed?.code || parsed?.errorCode || parsed?.statusCode
```

👉 现实世界：

返回可能是：

```json
{ "error": { "code": 1234, "message": "blocked" } }
```

或：

```json
{ "msg": "too many requests" }
```

甚至：

```html
<html>403 forbidden</html>
```

---

## 🚨 后果

```ts
upstreamCode = undefined
```

👉 你失去了：

* 风控识别能力
* 自动调度依据

---

## ✅ 建议升级

```ts
const detectUpstreamCode = (body: string) => {
  try {
    const parsed = JSON.parse(body);

    return (
      parsed?.code ||
      parsed?.errorCode ||
      parsed?.statusCode ||
      parsed?.error?.code ||
      parsed?.error?.type ||
      parsed?.message
    );
  } catch {
    if (body.includes("403")) return "HTTP_403";
    if (body.includes("429")) return "HTTP_429";
    return undefined;
  }
};
```

